WEBVTT

00:00.831 --> 00:02.221
Who is this guy?
What is he doing?

00:02.350 --> 00:05.038
He's watching, which is why we
refer to him as the observer.

00:05.197 --> 00:06.430
Previously on fringe...

00:06.534 --> 00:07.901
That's a different guy.

00:07.997 --> 00:09.405
Who are these people?

00:09.495 --> 00:13.678
I think these guys show up
at important moments.

00:14.773 --> 00:15.925
You were dead, Peter.

00:16.989 --> 00:19.646
We were drowning
and he dove in.

00:20.689 --> 00:23.305
We were saved, both of us,
by a man that I had never met.

00:23.372 --> 00:26.441
The boy is important.
He has to live.

00:26.509 --> 00:28.043
I have said too much.

00:28.110 --> 00:29.711
I'm not supposed
to get involved.

00:29.779 --> 00:32.347
It appears you've been busy.

00:32.415 --> 00:33.782
You have changed the future.

00:33.849 --> 00:37.319
You need to restore balance.
How?

00:37.386 --> 00:39.788
You will have an opportunity

00:39.855 --> 00:41.957
to fix this.

00:42.024 --> 00:44.759
Please don't take my son.

00:46.000 --> 00:52.074
